<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_CAS_IdentityPersonality_TraitsAspirations" s="315400">
  <T n="name">0x31F58DEC<!--String: "Traits & Aspirations"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_TraitsAndAspirations_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:49eaa7deb97cd8a6</T>
      <T n="text">0xC0A1D4C1<!--String: "What’s going on inside your Sim’s head? Their <b><font color='#199C2C'>Traits</font></b> define their personality, and their <b><font color='#199C2C'>Aspiration</font></b> gives them goals and dreams!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_TraitsAndAspiration_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1fdc8f512325c40c</T>
      <T n="text">0x9B195F48<!--String: "To customize your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>personality</font></b>, select a Pick a Trait button and pick Traits until all Trait slots are filled. These Traits affect everything in the game from Emotions and Skills to Hobbies and Relationships.\n\nSome Traits can't be <b><font color='#199C2C'>paired</font></b> with other Traits. For example, you can't be both Good and Evil. \n\nSome traits may be more <b><font color='#199C2C'>challenging</font></b> to play with, but they will provide unique opportunities for your Sims!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_TraitsAndAspiration_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:1fdc8f512325c40d</T>
      <T n="text">0xB39EFCF9<!--String: "A Sim’s Aspiration is what they aspire to be, do, and experience! Sims will be given <b><font color='#199C2C'>goals</font></b> based on their Aspiration that can be completed for <b><font color='#199C2C'>rewards</font></b>. \n\nSelect the Pick an Aspiration button to pick your first <b><font color='#199C2C'>Aspiration</font></b>. Most Aspiration <b><font color='#199C2C'>categories</font></b> have multiple options. For instance, click on Food and choose between Master Chef and Master Mixologist!\n\nYour first Aspiration will also give your Sim a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Bonus Trait</font></b> that you can see next to your selected Aspiration!"--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
